      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIL MISS CRITTER (4) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Tough Call (17.66) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up this time. WHAT'S IT ABOUT (5) is a Sarah Fellowes-trained newcomer by Barcia Bale out of Fava Monelli with no trial form to work with. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. FLAKY PIE (2) is a handily bred pup making her debut without a trial. Worth keeping a close eye on the market. CASUAL ALEX (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
